# Keep in touch

If you don't already follow us on Bluesky, please do so:
https://bsky.app/profile/torproject.org.

For support and exchange with our community, [the Tor Forum is the best place
to be](https://forum.torproject.org/). And the Tor Blog and newsletter are
still the most reliable source of Tor news. So, [please encourage others to
join our mailing list](https://donate.torproject.org/subscribe/) by sharing
this email.
